Class Jukebox

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Jukebox
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Jukebox
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A Jukebox keeps track of a song selection, all of its users, and what day it is. Plays songs as requested by a Student and sends/recieves messages with a Day object to ensure the song is allowed to be played.
    Author:
    Michelle Monteith and Jamie David
    See Also:
